    {
      "type": "conversation",
      "title": "Conversation Practice 1（会話）: At the Hospital",
      "context": "Talking to a doctor.",
      "lines": [
        {
          "spk": "A",
          "jp": "今日は どうしましたか。",
          "en": "What is wrong today? (Lit: How did you do?)",
          "terms": [
            "v_kyou",
            { "id": "v_suru", "form": "polite_mashita" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "spk": "B",
          "jp": "先生、頭が いたいです。少し 気分も わるいです。",
          "en": "Doctor, my head hurts. I also feel a little unwell.",
          "terms": [
            "v_sensei",
            "k_atama",
            { "id": "v_itai", "form": "polite_adj" },
            "v_kibun",
            { "id": "v_warui", "form": "polite_adj" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "spk": "A",
          "jp": "病気ですね。この 薬を 飲んで ください。",
          "en": "It is an illness. Please drink this medicine.",
          "terms": [
            { "id": "v_byouki", "form": "polite_adj" },
            "v_kusuri",
            { "id": "v_nomu", "form": "te_form" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "spk": "B",
          "jp": "分かりました。ありがとうございます。",
          "en": "I understand. Thank you.",
          "terms": [
            { "id": "v_wakaru", "form": "polite_mashita" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "conversation",
      "title": "Conversation Practice 2（会話）: Career Path",
      "context": "Discussing future studies.",
      "lines": [
        {
          "spk": "A",
          "jp": "大学院で 何を 学びますか。",
          "en": "What do you study at graduate school?",
          "terms": [
            "v_daigakuin",
            { "id": "v_manabu", "form": "polite_masu" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "spk": "B",
          "jp": "医学を 学びます。医者に なりたいですから。",
          "en": "I study medical science. Because I want to become a doctor.",
          "terms": [
            "v_igaku",
            { "id": "v_manabu", "form": "polite_masu" },
            "v_isha"
          ]
        },
        {
          "spk": "A",
          "jp": "いいですね。父も 医者でした。",
          "en": "That is good. My father was a doctor too.",
          "terms": [
            "k_chichi","v_isha"
          ]
        },
        {
          "spk": "B",
          "jp": "大きい 病院で 働きましたか。",
          "en": "Did he work at a big hospital?",
          "terms": [
            "v_ookii",
            "v_byouin",
            { "id": "v_hataraku", "form": "polite_mashita" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "conversation",
      "title": "Conversation Practice 3（会話）: Bad Eyesight",
      "context": "Buying medicine.",
      "lines": [
        {
          "spk": "A",
          "jp": "すみません。目薬は ありますか。",
          "en": "Excuse me. Do you have eye medicine (drops)?",
          "terms": [
            "v_megusuri",
            { "id": "v_aru", "form": "polite_masu" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "spk": "B",
          "jp": "はい、あります。目が いたいですか。",
          "en": "Yes, we do. Do your eyes hurt?",
          "terms": [
            "k_me",
            { "id": "v_aru", "form": "polite_masu" },
            { "id": "v_itai", "form": "polite_adj" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "spk": "A",
          "jp": "いいえ、いたくありません。でも、赤いです。",
          "en": "No, they do not hurt. But, they are red.",
          "terms": [
            { "id": "v_akai", "form": "polite_adj" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "spk": "B",
          "jp": "そうですか。これを 使って ください。",
          "en": "Is that so. Please use this.",
          "terms": [
            { "id": "v_tsukau", "form": "te_form" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "conversation",
      "title": "Conversation Practice 4（会話）: Sad News",
      "context": "Discussing a pet.",
      "lines": [
        {
          "spk": "A",
          "jp": "金魚は 元気ですか。",
          "en": "Is your goldfish healthy?",
          "terms": [
            "v_kingyo",
            { "id": "v_genki", "form": "polite_adj" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "spk": "B",
          "jp": "いいえ、きのう 死にました。",
          "en": "No, it died yesterday.",
          "terms": [
            { "id": "v_shinu", "form": "polite_mashita" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "spk": "A",
          "jp": "えっ、病気でしたか。",
          "en": "Eh? Was it sick?",
          "terms": [
            { "id": "v_byouki", "form": "polite_past_adj" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "spk": "B",
          "jp": "はい。病死です。",
          "en": "Yes. It was death from illness.",
          "terms": [
            "v_byoushi"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "reading",
      "title": "Reading Practice 1: A Long Life",
      "passage": [
        {
          "jp": "有名な 学者が いました。",
          "en": "There was a famous scholar.",
          "terms": [
            "v_yuumei","v_gakusha",
            { "id": "v_iru", "form": "polite_mashita" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "jp": "この 人は たくさんの 本を 書きました。",
          "en": "This person wrote many books.",
          "terms": ["k_hito",
            "k_hon",
            { "id": "v_kaku", "form": "polite_mashita" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "jp": "先月、病院で 死にました。",
          "en": "Last month, he died at the hospital.",
          "terms": [
            "v_sengetsu",
            "v_byouin",
            { "id": "v_shinu", "form": "polite_mashita" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "jp": "病死ではありません。古くて 長い 人生でした。",
          "en": "It was not death from illness. It was an old and long life.",
          "terms": [
            "v_byoushi",
            { "id": "v_furui", "form": "te_form" },
            "v_nagai",
            "v_jinsei"
          ]
        },
        {
          "jp": "死者ですが、本は ずっと あります。",
          "en": "He is a deceased person, but his books will exist forever.",
          "terms": [
            "v_shisha",
            "k_hon",
            { "id": "v_aru", "form": "polite_masu" }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "questions": [
        {
          "q": "学者は 何を しましたか。",
          "a": "本を 書きました。",
          "terms": ["v_gakusha",
            "k_hon",
            { "id": "v_kaku", "form": "polite_mashita" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "q": "どこで 死にましたか。",
          "a": "病院で 死にました。",
          "terms": [
            "v_byouin",
            { "id": "v_shinu", "form": "polite_mashita" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "q": "病気でしたか。",
          "a": "いいえ、病死ではありません。",
          "terms": [
            "v_byouki",
            "v_byoushi"
          ]
        },
        {
          "q": "どんな 人生 でしたか。",
          "a": "古くて 長い 人生でした。",
          "terms": [
            { "id": "v_furui", "form": "te_form" },
            "v_nagai",
            "v_jinsei"
          ]
        }
      ]
